Metadynamics
Alessandro Barducci ,
Massimiliano Bonomi ,
Michele Parrinello ,
Computational Science, Department of Chemistry and Applied Biosciences, ETH Zurich, USI Campus, Lugano, Switzerland
First published: 18 February 2011
https://doi.org/10.1002/wcms.31
Citations: 665
OpenURL University Of Massachusetts
Sections
PDF PDF
Tools
